The paper focuses on developing a new algorithm for deep reinforcement learning that improves sample efficiency and learning performance through efficient exploration of the learning environment. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), control systems (cs.SY), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
